Package com.facebook.buck.android.resources

Class ResTablePackage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.android.resources.ResChunk
      • com.facebook.buck.android.resources.ResTablePackage
  • public class ResTablePackage
extends ResChunk
    A Package consists of a header: ResTable_header u16 chunk_type u16 header_size u32 chunk_size u32 package_id u16[128] name u32 typeStringOffset u32 lastPublicTypeOffset u32 keyStringOffset u32 lastPublicKeyOffset u32 typeIdOffset

    The header is followed by a types string pool (containing types like "id", "attr", "drawable", ...) and a keys string pool (containing the names of resources). Then follows a TypeSpec for each type (# of types can be derived from the size of the types stringpool).
